{  System Settings Dialog                                                       }
{       This dialog is *highly* dependant on the operation system as to what    }
{       the title of the page may be.                                           }
{               This is Win2k sp 2                                              }
{               General      = 0                                                }
{               Network ID   = 1                                                }
{               Hardware     = 2                                                }
{               User Profile = 3                                                }
{               Advanced     = 4                                                }
{       WinXP has several more, WinNT4 different names etc.                     }
